🧰 Tools & Technologies Used
🧠 AI & Frameworks
IBM Watsonx.ai – Agent development platform

IBM Granite / Mistral LLM – Language models for response generation

LangGraph – Agent orchestration framework

ReAct architecture – Reasoning + action flow for agents

RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) – Grounded AI responses

📄 Knowledge & Vectorization
IBM Watsonx Vector Index – Document-based vector search

PDFs/Text files – Nutrition knowledge base used for grounding

In-Memory Vector Store / Milvus (optional) – For storing embeddings

🛠️ Tools & Services
IBM Cloud Lite – Cloud infrastructure

Watsonx Agent Builder – Visual interface to configure and deploy agent

Google Search Tool / DuckDuckGo Search – Web tool for external info (optional)


